Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:23.49,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那就保护他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:26.93,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这才能表现我们的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:33.81,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}从今天起我最勇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:37.48,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:40.01,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强者出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:46.88,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}从今天起我最酷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:53.02,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}崭新的最强的NO.1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.88,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:03:02.97,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}的确从今天起 我就是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:14.10,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夢ならあるはずだ　あなたにも僕にでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:14.10,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每个人都有梦想 你我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:22.38,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}見つかりにくいだけだ忙しすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:22.38,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但因为太忙而很难被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:34.67,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ミエナイチカラで　だれもが強く繋がっている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:34.67,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}谁都被看不到的力量强力的连接着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:39.80,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何も大したことじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:39.80,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:44.52,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そばにいても離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:44.52,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无论是否在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:49.33,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}昨日　今日　明日と
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:49.33,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}昨天 今天 明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:22:02.24,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔のあなたはいつでも　この胸にいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:22:02.24,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的笑容永远深印在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:06.90,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You've got to be strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:09.39,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's never too late
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:13.37,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I never say die
